title: LF Ranked 5's Team Gold 3 ADC and Silver 5 Support
body: Hey we're a duo looking to get the ward skins for ranked 5v5's, leave comment if ur interested, we're planning on playing pretty late tonight

replies.body: Same goes, pretty solid Gold V mid top laner who can stretch into jungle and support, perform best on assassins (fizz, zed, veigar) and Azir in mid and rumble/renek/gnar top lane, but can play almost anyone.

Yeah i'm keen, i'll likely be up being nocturnal while ~~studying~~ procrastinating for Botany finals so i'll be keen to play a couple of games. I'm a Silver 4 Mid and Top main (mostly mid) with a huge champ pool on mid shoot me a friend request if you're interested .
